# Keep the build context small and deterministic (#39): without this, the
# images' `COPY . .` drags in the host's dev node_modules (overwriting the
# alpine-native install from the deps stage), the multi-GB Rust target/, and
# .git — making local builds slow and host-dependent.
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
target
**/dist
# Without dist, a stale host tsbuildinfo makes the in-image tsc a silent no-op
# (incremental "up to date" → nothing emitted → downstream packages can't
# resolve @scadium/shared).
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.next
**/.turbo
*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# Local Solana validator ledger + Anchor artifacts (#81): test-ledger holds a
# unix socket (admin.rpc — breaks tar) and ~hundreds of MB of rocksdb data,
# bloating the build context. Never needed in the image.
test-ledger
**/test-ledger
.anchor
**/*.so
